{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was among the other group from the kitchen, the only Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I saw, with my eyes, I witnessed a party like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had, very often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was, you know, a special building when-- when you entered the factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factory was a building by itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was, you know, where offices were and where the-- his apartment and the ballroom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were working over there until mid-summer of 1944, when the-- when the Russian forces were coming forward.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most of the camps all around were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schindler's factory was also liquidated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there came the order, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No more work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No more nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they rounded up us again, put on open trucks, and we were brought back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Plaszow I had, again, an unbelievable experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was not the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I am here with you speaking about my own experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we were brought back to Plaszow, when I was assigned with other women-- whole groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were men working and women working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were assigned to reopen the mass graves, carrying the remains that they were buried-- some for longer time and some only recent-- we were carrying the remains to a certain square where there were wooden boards.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were throwing the remains over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Nazi ordered-- Jews were ordered to pour gasoline over it and burn this to ashes because we know for a fact, the Nazis tried to erase as much evidence as possible what was going on in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, they couldn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You cannot wipe out all the evidence, no matter how hard you try.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Number one-- they did not succeed because there were many things, many signs afterwards.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
